WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.200
[Mission control hums as the launch bay lights wake up.]

00:00:02.200 --> 00:00:04.600
[Captain Nova advances toward the rocket as launch systems glow blue and amber.]

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:07.200
[The rocket surges into a bright star corridor and accelerates into space.]

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:10.042
[Captain Nova reaches a luminous new world as the mission briefing prepares to open.]
